---
import MiFoto from "../../assets/img/vishal.png";
---

<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row"
>
  <!-- Image -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={MiFoto.src}
      alt="Vishal Rawal"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Vishal Rawal</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-4">
      I am a passionate Web Developer focused on creating modern, responsive,
      and user-friendly web applications. I enjoy building clean and engaging
      digital experiences using technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript,
      React, Astro, and Tailwind CSS.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
      My interest in technology and programming started through curiosity and
      grew into a strong passion for web development. I continuously explore
      new technologies, improve my development skills, and work on practical
      projects that help me gain real-world experience.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
      I am committed to continuous learning, problem-solving, and creating
      impactful digital solutions. My goal is to become a skilled MERN Stack
      Developer and contribute to innovative software projects while delivering
      high-quality user experiences.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>